1. **Analyze and Describe the Main Target Image:**

The main image shows two separate structures built from blocks.

* **Structure 1 (Tower):**  Composed of 5 blocks.  Two orange/red blocks form the base, one yellow/gold block sits on top of those forming a column and then two similar-colored angled blocks forming the roof.  It appears to have 3 layers.

* **Structure 2 (Bridge/Group):**  Composed of 7 blocks.  This structure consists of a base of orange/red blocks, a yellow arched block above them. Then a blue cube on the right edge. Further blocks stacked in a variety of colors and shapes. It seems to have 3 layers.
